{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/targetcoordinate"]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/targetCoordinate"},"metadata":{"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L752","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)targetCoordinate","roleHeading":"Instance Property","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"targetCoordinate"}],"symbolKind":"property","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"targetCoordinate","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"targetCoordinate","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"assign","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D","text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"targetCoordinate","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"By default, this property is set to an invalid coordinate, indicating that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"there is no target. In course tracking mode, the target forms one of two foci","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"in the viewport, the other being the user location annotation. Typically, this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"property is set to a destination or waypoint in a real-time navigation scene.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"As the user annotation moves toward the target, the map automatically zooms in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to fit both foci optimally within the viewport.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This property has no effect if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userTrackingMode"},{"type":"text","text":" property is set to a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"value other than "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Changing the value of this property updates the map view with an animated"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"transition. If you don’t want to animate the change, use the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"-setTargetCoordinate:animated:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" method instead."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The geographic coordinate that is the subject of observation as the user"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"location is being tracked."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/targetCoordinate":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/targetCoordinate","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The geographic coordinate that is the subject of observation as the user"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"location is being tracked."}],"type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"targetCoordinate","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"targetCoordinate","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/targetcoordinate"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/